JOHANNESBURG - Doctor Mbuyiseni Ndlozi acquired his doctorate in the Philosophy in Political Studies from the University of the Witwatersrand on Monday. At the graduation ceremony, Ndlozi was flanked by the top leadership of the Economic Freedom Fighters (EFF), all dressed in their graduation gowns.  Ndlozi was reportedly raised only by his single mother and met his estranged father for the first time only recently. eNCA